title: dwdeclare - discography
description:
This torrent contains both albums by Canada's greatest do-it-yourself garage musician, dwdeclare (aka theveganarchist). 

all my best (2011)
anonypuss (2012)
 
He first achieved notoriety on YouTube in 2010 with his breakthrough smash hit The Amino Acid Song and the rest is history. Listen for yourself what the critics and fans alike are raving about. This music will change your every thought pattern and recalibrate your place in the universe. Pure Art, pure pleasure, pure life!

"dwdeclare's music is stardust, it is golden, it will get you back to the garden."
